	[em 
		"Space Battle
	]em
	" is a space shooter game that came bundled in the Intellivision 25 Video Game System. It is a stripped down port of the game of the same name for the original Intellivision game console. While most of the basic gameplay mechanics have been retained — command space fighter squadrons to eliminate hostile alien armadas — the finer details have been noticeably simplified. The most notable difference is that squadrons do not engage in battle outside of the main shooting screen, which means that input cannot be ended early like with the 
	(__wikiLink|displaytext=original game|href=/4418M)
	".
